item.title: Runescape classic just got updated
item.dc:creator: @undead666 undead666
item.description:
@undead666 wrote:

Super_ as you most likely see, they have basicly used a 194-420- loader, and made it read the client as a RsPack200,

Decied to make a updater along with the update on rsc

[code]- Model
^ hb implements interface com.bot.accessors.Model

  • GameImage MiddleMan
    ^ mb implements interface com.bot.accessors.GameImageMiddleMan

  • GameWindow
    ^ ba implements interface com.bot.accessors.GameWindow

  • Camera
    ^ a implements interface com.bot.accessors.Camera

  • Engine Handle
    ^ kb implements interface com.bot.accessors.EngineHandle

  • Packet Construction
    ^ ca implements interface com.bot.accessors.PacketConstruction

  • Game Image
    ^ la implements interface com.bot.accessors.GameImage

  • Sound
    ^ t implements interface com.bot.accessors.Sound

  • mudclient
    ^ client implements interface com.bot.accessors.mudclient

Update completed in 0:0:0
[/code]

To hook, aa class = GameWindow
And some fields but its now 4am so nighty nighty

P.s they have also changed the way the cache is loaded same format as the current runescape
